content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #85103 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
This ICE requires using internal rustc attributes, but I'm prioritizing it because it blocks a piece of a rustdoc feature.
I've tried bisecting but I went far back in time, does it make sense to you @Camelid or you were expecting a more recent culprit?
I didn't even know if it was a regression :)
@Camelid how much does this issue impacts rustdoc? I would assign a p-medium but I'm undecided if that would end of with blocking rustdoc works in some ways
(reason is: being a nightly-only flag, probably p-medium is right)
bumping a bit the priority, this seems to be annoying T-rustdoc
